DescriptionData.Title: Headphone Stand / Headset Holder / Desk Display Hanger Under-Desk Headphone Stand Mount Wooden Headphone Hanger Holder with Adhesive Sticky for Home and Office

Holds securly under your desk surface using strong 3M VBH tape

Compatible Headphones:
- Bose QuietComfort QC3, QC2, QC15, QC25, AE, AE2, TP-1, Soundtrue
- Grado SR60, SR80, M1, SR225, SR325, RA2, RS1

- AKG K518, K518DJ, K81, K520
- JBL, TMG81W, TMG81B, ON-EAR J03B, J03S Tempo
- SONY MDR-XB900, MDR-XB910, MDR-XB920, MDR-7506, MDR-V6
- Sennheiser HD-201, HD-202 II , RS0120
- Parrot Zik
- Beats Studio, Solo, Solo2
And many other headphones

Note:
- Headphone stand only, Headphone is not included.

Package Includes:
- 1 x Headphone Stand
